title: Digital Art - Full Year 2018 Collection
description: http://ititli.com/images/ILco0zr.png Digital Art Live is a stunning showcase of some of the best digital art in the sci-fi and fantasy genres beautifully presented in our new monthly magazine. It follows the same format as our previous publication 3D Art Direct. It’s all about the “behind the scenes of art” by featuring in-depth interviews with the artists. You will discover what inspired the artists, the steps they made in conceptualising their work and the techniques they used in building their creations. We examine 3D and 2D digital art as well as mixed mode. In essence it’ s capturing stunning artwork alongside fascinating stories of creativity. Digital Art Live - Full Year 2018 Collection English | 10 issues | True PDF | 575 MB
